00:12:26.800 --> 00:12:31.200
Subtitles facilitate the translation 
of the original language medium

00:12:31.200 --> 00:12:37.280
into other languages. Today, I've 
provided subtitles which are being

00:12:37.280 --> 00:12:42.720
