00:13:46.080 --> 00:13:51.760
in a multicultural and multilingual world. 
Your customers and stakeholders in your

00:13:51.760 --> 00:13:56.160
target locations are likely to come 
from different language backgrounds

00:13:56.800 --> 00:14:04.160
and have varying levels of fluency. Trends show 
that the world's increasing appetite for online

00:14:04.160 --> 00:14:09.920
learning is matched by its demand for being 
