00:14:48.400 --> 00:14:54.000
surrounds us on public transport, shared offices,
or wherever we choose to access the information.

00:14:56.320 --> 00:15:01.600
There may be times when it's helpful to 
watch a video individually or as a group without

00:15:01.600 --> 00:15:07.680
the sound on in places where background noise may 
make it impossible to have sound at audible levels.

00:15:08.960 --> 00:15:11.840
Please think about those occasions 
